<section id="contato" class="section-padding bg-[#1A1A1A] relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Subtle decorative circles -->
  <div class="absolute -right-20 -top-20 h-96 w-96 rounded-full bg-[#C5A059]/10 blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute -left-20 -bottom-20 h-96 w-96 rounded-full bg-[#C5A059]/5 blur-3xl"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 text-center lg:px-8">
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.6em] text-[#C5A059]">
        Agenda Exclusiva
      </span>
      <h2 class="mt-8 text-5xl font-medium leading-tight text-white sm:text-7xl tracking-tighter">
        Pronta Para <br />
        <span class="italic font-light">Sua Transformação?</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-10 text-xl leading-relaxed text-white/50 font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Agende uma consulta avaliativa personalizada e descubra como a biomedicina estética pode elevar sua autoestima e bem-estar.
      </p>
      
      <div class="mt-14 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-10">
        <a href="https://wa.me/5511999999999" target="_blank" class="btn-elegant bg-[#C5A059] hover:bg-[#A68546]">
          Falar Diretamente com a Dra.
        </a>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/30">
          <span>Atendimento Boutique</span>
          <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[#C5A059]"></span>
          <span>Itaim Bibi, SP</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
